{"tid":1766362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"1118 油尖旺慘烈一役.  我個人較相信 OVER 150 名傷者, 亦估計當晚應該有死到人","createTime":"2019-12-02T13:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T13:54:34.000Z","uid":237465,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fdbaa03c7434f76a684da89ec165784300f863a0","tid":1766362,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T13:50:28.000Z","msg":"1118 油尖旺慘烈一役.  我個人較相信 OVER 150 名傷者, 亦估計當晚應該有死到人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">血海深仇<br />\n</span></span><br />\n上月 18 日大批市民於油麻地聚集，希望「營救」被圍困於理大的人，有片段顯示警方驅散市民時用輕型貨車衝向人群，有指引發「人踩人」。《立場新聞》今日收到一份，相信是消防處行動紀錄的文件，顯示消防當日需要超過兩個半小時，方能分流傷者，期間消防要「等待警方分流」。文件亦紀錄有傷者因沒有警察押送而未能即時送院，有警員要求先將 41 名傷勢較輕的傷者送往警署，而非送院治療。<br />\n<br />\n原文請按 LINK<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B2%B9%E9%BA%BB%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%BA%E8%B8%A9%E4%BA%BA-%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E7%96%91%E5%9B%A0-%E7%AD%89%E5%BE%85%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-%E8%8A%B1%E9%80%BE%E5%85%A9%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E5%88%86%E6%B5%81%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85-%E8%AD%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85%E7%9B%B4%E9%80%81%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B8%25A9%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%259B%25A0-%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%25BE%2585%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E8%258A%25B1%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%25B5%2581%25E5%2582%25B7%25E8%2580%2585-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%2582%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%259B%25B4%25E9%2580%2581%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%2F&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRfrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=458c4c4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%